short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Makes it possible to sign in to the Rustalytics app in the web browser.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension is used to pair Rustalytics with Rust+.

To use this extension: go to Rustalytics.com/app and click on the login button that appears if you have the extension installed.

After a successful sign-in you can pair servers with Rustalytics.
